Coders will be givin spot as admins on the server, and the rest will be granted to be mods.

~Mods~ (Will be edited when the rest are filled)

~Forum/Web design and managers~ - OMG - I AM NOOB
[b]Current Project[/b]: A PK area, Was hoping we could get the duel arena and make it PVP. Detials: Make it so the only way you can get out is running out of the duel arena. Ground floor of the duel arena is all pk, and they can't tele out. They can teleport in, but not out.
Everyone is welcome to register.
Anyways, thats about it. JOIN NOW! :)
